text: The 2090s is a decade in the Anno Domini and Common Era in the Gregorian calendar. It will begin on January 1, 2090 and end on December 31, 2099. It is distinct from the decade known as the 210th decade which will begin on January 1, 2091 and end on December 31, 2100. ==Notable predictions and known events== *August 6, 2091 - 100th anniversary of the Internet *December 26, 2091 - 100th anniversary of the Dissolution of the Soviet Union *February 29, 2096 - the last leap year until 2104 because 2100 is not a leap year.
